edu.wscc.group4.group2assignment6.models

Class TipCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wscc.group4.group2assignment6.models.TipCalculator

  • public class TipCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Calculator that takes in a bill amount, amount of Guests, and a Percentage of a tip and can calculate the total amount of the bill including tip,
    the tip amount, and the amount each guess will owe for the tip and for the total amount including tip. Created by Levi on 2/17/2018.
